bilingual.source: Shall I be believed when I say that, at the depth of thirty feet, I could see as if I was in broad daylight?
bilingual.target: 当我说在三十英尺深处，我能看得像在白天一样清楚时，你会相信吗？

bilingual.source: He swims in the depth of the lake.
They work in the depth of the mine.
bilingual.target: 他们在矿井的深处工作。

bilingual.source: She got lost in the depth of the forest.
bilingual.target: 她在森林的深处迷路了。

bilingual.source: We need to understand the depth of the problem.
bilingual.target: 我们需要了解问题的深处。

bilingual.source: This book explores the depth of human psychology.
bilingual.target: 这本书探讨了人类心理的深处。

bilingual.source: But suddenly Laura did not feel any fear anymore and within a second she jumped into the air and fell into the endless depth of the Grand Canyon.
bilingual.target: 但是突然劳拉不再感到任何恐惧，不到一秒钟，她就跳到了空中，掉进了大峡谷无尽的深处。

bilingual.source: Search in the depth of the fussed ocean.

bilingual.target: 是穿过黑暗的迷宫般的深处，
是穿过黑暗的迷宫般的深处。

yingyinNormal.en: Depending on the depth, that's either a proctologist or a general surgeon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那要取决于深度，要么是直肠科医师，要么是外科医生。

yingyinNormal.en: Tell me. At what point did he realize the depth of your indifference towards him? I‘m not indifferent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 告诉我，他是什么时候开始彻底明白了你对他其实是根本不在乎的？我没不在乎他。

yingyinNormal.en: The depth of Eurus's psychosis and the extent of her abilities couldn't hope to be contained in any ordinary institution.
yingyinNormal.zh: 欧罗斯严重的精神疾病和她高超的能力，让她不可能待在普通的病院里。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, I'm warning you, I can play this game, too. If it's like your 3-D chess game, then you're out of your length, width and depth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，我警告你，你玩的小把戏的我也会玩。如果你玩小把戏和玩三维象棋的水准一样，那你可是在三个维度上都不自量力。

yingyinNormal.en: Like the ale I used to flavor the bread I made for Justin and Howard, this bread uses another by-product of brewing, malt extract, to give it sweetness and depth of flavor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就像我给贾斯汀和霍华德做的面包用啤酒来提味一样，这种面包用到另一种额外的东西，麦芽糖提取物，会增加甜味和色泽。

yingyinNormal.en: I thank you for allowing me to be a part of your conclusion of this chapter of your lives and the commencement of your next chapter to say that I'm honored doesn't even begin to quantify the depth of gratitude that really companies an honorary doctorate from Harvard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 感谢你们，让我有机会与你们共度人生这一华丽篇章的谢幕时刻并开启新的篇章。仅仅用荣幸一词无法表达出我对同时授予我的哈佛大学荣誉博士学位的感激之情。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Yet its report may well set back reform by obscuring the <highlight>depth</highlight> and breadth of the challenge that Congress asked it to illuminate.
